seu\'\'|komeaning=Transliteration of Japanese name\n|zh_cmn=怪河馬 \'\'Guài Hé Mǎ\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=Literally "Strange hippopotamus".\n|ru=Гиппопотас \'\'Gippopotas\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* {{DL|Recurring wild Pokémon in the anime|Hippopotas|Hippopotas (anime)}}\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Ground}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Ground|prevnum=448|prev=Lucario|nextnum=450|next=Hippowdon}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[Category:Ranger Partner Pokémon]]\n\n[[de:Hippopotas]]\n[[es:Hippopotas]]\n[[fr:Hippopotas]]\n[[it:Hippopotas]]\n[[ja:ヒポポタス]]\n[[zh:沙河马]]'}